---
import BaseLayout from "../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Children's Eye Exam in Tijuana | Ópticas Jarmar"
  description="Pediatric eye exam in Tijuana from age 3. Special child-friendly protocol, early detection for better school performance. Ópticas Jarmar."
>
  <style>
    :root { --bg: #071A3E; --surface: #0D2B6B; --accent: #3A8FE0; }

    .hero { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg) 0%, var(--surface) 100%); color: #fff; padding: 100px 20px 80px; text-align: center; }
    .hero-tag { display: inline-block; background: rgba(58,143,224,0.2); border: 1px solid var(--accent); color: var(--accent); border-radius: 100px; padding: 6px 18px; font-size: 0.85rem; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .hero h1 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem); font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .hero h1 span { color: var(--accent); }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.15rem; opacity: 0.85; max-width: 620px; margin: 0 auto 36px; line-height: 1.7; }
    .btn-cta { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; background: var(--accent); color: #fff; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 100px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; text-decoration: none; transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.2s; }
    .btn-cta:hover { opacity: 0.9; transform: translateY(-2px); }

    .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }
    .section { padding: 72px 20px; }
    .section:nth-child(even) { background: #f7f9fc; }
    .section-title { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.2rem); font-weight: 700; color: var(--bg); margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .section-title span { color: var(--accent); }
    .section-sub { color: #4a5568; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 36px; }

    .razones { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; }
    .razon { background: #fff; border-radius: 18px; border: 1.5px solid rgba(58,143,224,0.2); padding: 28px 24px; text-align: center; }
    .razon-icon { font-size: 2.4rem; margin-bottom: 14px; display: block; }
    .razon h4 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--bg); margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .razon p { color: #4a5568; font-size: 0.97rem; line-height: 1.65; }

    .alertas { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr)); gap: 16px; }
    .alerta { background: var(--surface); color: #fff; border-radius: 14px; padding: 20px 18px; display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: flex-start; }
    .alerta-icon { font-size: 1.5rem; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }
    .alerta p { font-size: 0.95rem; opacity: 0.9; line-height: 1.5; }

    .examen-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 16px; }
    .examen-list li { background: #fff; border: 1.5px solid rgba(58,143,224,0.25); border-radius: 14px; padding: 18px 20px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; font-size: 1rem; color: #2d3748; line-height: 1.5; }
    .examen-list li::before { content: "✓"; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }

    .edades-box { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg) 0%, var(--surface) 100%); border-radius: 24px; color: #fff; padding: 40px; text-align: center; }
    .edades-box h3 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .edades-row { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; }
    .edad-chip { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3); border-radius: 100px; padding: 8px 20px; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; }

    .cta-section { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg) 0%, var(--surface) 100%); color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 80px 20px; }
    .cta-section h2 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .cta-section p { font-size: 1.1rem; opacity: 0.85; margin-bottom: 36px; max-width: 560px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }

    .back-link { display: block; text-align: center; padding: 28px; color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; }
    .back-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  </style>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="hero-tag">Children's vision · Tijuana</span>
      <h1>Children's Eye Exam<br>in <span>Tijuana</span></h1>
      <p>Vision is the foundation of learning. We detect visual problems in children from age 3 with a protocol designed especially for them.</p>
      <a href="https://wa.me/526645791970?text=Hello%2C+I%27d+like+to+schedule+a+children%27s+eye+exam+at+%C3%93pticas+Jarmar+Tijuana." target="_blank" class="btn-cta">
        Book exam →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Why check your child's<br><span>eyes</span>?</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">80% of school learning comes through vision. A child with undetected visual problems may be incorrectly labeled as having learning difficulties.</p>
      <div class="razones">
        <div class="razon">
          <span class="razon-icon">📚</span>
          <h4>School performance</h4>
          <p>Undetected myopia, hyperopia, or astigmatism can affect reading, writing, and attention in class.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="razon">
          <span class="razon-icon">🧠</span>
          <h4>Early development</h4>
          <p>Vision develops until age 8. Detecting problems before then allows for more effective correction.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="razon">
          <span class="razon-icon">👁️</span>
          <h4>Lazy eye (amblyopia)</h4>
          <p>If not detected and treated in time, a lazy eye can cause permanent vision loss in that eye.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="razon">
          <span class="razon-icon">🎯</span>
          <h4>Kids don't complain</h4>
          <p>Children don't know they see poorly because they think everyone sees the same way. Only an exam can detect it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title"><span>Warning signs</span> in your child</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">If you notice any of these signs in your child, it's time to book a vision exam.</p>
      <div class="alertas">
        <div class="alerta"><span class="alerta-icon">👀</span><p>Gets very close to screens or books</p></div>
        <div class="alerta"><span class="alerta-icon">😖</span><p>Frowns or squints to see clearly</p></div>
        <div class="alerta"><span class="alerta-icon">📺</span><p>Sits very close to the TV</p></div>
        <div class="alerta"><span class="alerta-icon">✏️</span><p>Difficulty copying from the board</p></div>
        <div class="alerta"><span class="alerta-icon">😫</span><p>Gets tired quickly reading or has headaches</p></div>
        <div class="alerta"><span class="alerta-icon">↔️</span><p>One eye that turns or drifts to the side</p></div>
        <div class="alerta"><span class="alerta-icon">📉</span><p>Poor school performance with no apparent cause</p></div>
        <div class="alerta"><span class="alerta-icon">🏃</span><p>Clumsiness or difficulty with sports activities</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">What does the <span>pediatric exam</span> include?</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Our special protocol for children is friendly, non-invasive, and comprehensive. We use tools designed to make the visit a positive experience.</p>
      <ul class="examen-list">
        <li>Age-appropriate visual acuity testing</li>
        <li>Objective refraction without verbal responses needed</li>
        <li>Binocular vision and stereopsis evaluation</li>
        <li>Lazy eye (amblyopia) and strabismus detection</li>
        <li>Cornea, lens, and retina health check</li>
        <li>Ocular motility evaluation</li>
        <li>Non-contact tonometry for young children</li>
        <li>Full explanation and guidance for parents</li>
      </ul>

      <div style="margin-top: 40px;">
        <div class="edades-box">
          <h3>When should I bring my child?</h3>
          <div class="edades-row">
            <span class="edad-chip">Ages 3–4: First check-up</span>
            <span class="edad-chip">Ages 5–6: Before starting school</span>
            <span class="edad-chip">Ages 7–12: Annual exam</span>
            <span class="edad-chip">Teens: Every year or at each new school year</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Give your child the gift of seeing clearly</h2>
      <p>Book your child's eye exam at Ópticas Jarmar Tijuana. Specialized pediatric protocol in a calm, friendly environment.</p>
      <a href="https://wa.me/526645791970?text=Hello%2C+I%27d+like+to+schedule+a+children%27s+eye+exam+at+%C3%93pticas+Jarmar+Tijuana." target="_blank" class="btn-cta">
        Book via WhatsApp
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <a href="/en/tijuana/" class="back-link">← Back to Tijuana</a>
</BaseLayout>
